headline: Did CoStar’s Homes AI Launch on Homes.com Just Shift CoStar Group's (CSGP) Investment Narrative?
summary: Earlier this week, CoStar Group launched Homes AI on Homes.com, a Microsoft Azure OpenAI-powered tool that lets consumers search for properties via real-time, conversational voice or text, drawing on extensive in-house property, school, neighborhood, and 3D imaging data. By keeping all Homes AI data within its proprietary ecosystem and tailoring the system specifically for real estate, CoStar is positioning Homes.com as a differentiated, AI-driven marketplace experience that could influence...

headline: 3 Stocks That May Be Trading Below Estimated Value In February 2026
summary: As February 2026 begins, the U.S. stock market shows a robust start with major indices like the Dow Jones Industrial Average and S&P 500 posting significant gains. In this environment of renewed optimism, identifying stocks that may be trading below their estimated value can offer intriguing opportunities for investors looking to capitalize on potential growth amid favorable market conditions.
